<div id="main_content">
	<h2>A Thousand Robotics Competitors Due</h2>
	
	<p class="article_info">
		
			By Chad Binette
		
		<span class="date">March 10, 2004</span></p>
	
	
	
		<div class="article_img" style="width: px;">

			<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="../resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/0/NE199/en_US/040310robots1.jpg" height="" width=""  /> 
			
				<p class="photo_credit">Photo: File Photos: Kelly Petrik</p>
			
			<p>Robots try to knock down tubs, and the one to put the most tubs on the other guy's turf wins. </p>
			
				<p class="note"><a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=0024004112faeca0fb2b47ccbe006e64">Full Photo</a></p>
			
			
			
			
					
						
						
							
